17497
17498 unsigned mid;
17499 unsigned start = 0;
17500 unsigned end = 250;
17501 while (start < end) {
17502 mid = start + (end - start) / 2;
17503 if (Opcode == getFalsePredOpcodeTable[mid][0]) {
17504 break;
17505 }
17506 if (Opcode < getFalsePredOpcodeTable[mid][0])
17507 end = mid;
17508 else
17509 start = mid + 1;
17510 }
17511 if (start == end)
17512 return -1; // Instruction doesn't exist in this table.
17513
17514 return getFalsePredOpcodeTable[mid][1];

18105 { Hexagon::S4_pstorerinewfnew_rr, Hexagon::S4_pstorerinewf_rr },
18106 { Hexagon::S4_pstorerinewtnew_abs, Hexagon::S4_pstorerinewt_abs },
18107 { Hexagon::S4_pstorerinewtnew_io, Hexagon::S2_pstorerinewt_io },
18108 { Hexagon::S4_pstorerinewtnew_rr, Hexagon::S4_pstorerinewt_rr },
18109 { Hexagon::S4_pstoreritnew_abs, Hexagon::S4_pstorerit_abs },
18110 { Hexagon::S4_pstoreritnew_io, Hexagon::S2_pstorerit_io },
18111 { Hexagon::S4_pstoreritnew_rr, Hexagon::S4_pstorerit_rr },
18112 { Hexagon::S4_storeirbfnew_io, Hexagon::S4_storeirbf_io },
18113 { Hexagon::S4_storeirbtnew_io, Hexagon::S4_storeirbt_io },
18114 { Hexagon::S4_storeirhfnew_io, Hexagon::S4_storeirhf_io },
18115 { Hexagon::S4_storeirhtnew_io, Hexagon::S4_storeirht_io },
18116 { Hexagon::S4_storeirifnew_io, Hexagon::S4_storeirif_io },
18117 { Hexagon::S4_storeiritnew_io, Hexagon::S4_storeirit_io },
18118}; // End of getPredOldOpcodeTable
18119
18120 unsigned mid;
18121 unsigned start = 0;
18122 unsigned end = 162;
18123 while (start < end) {
18124 mid = start + (end - start) / 2;
18125 if (Opcode == getPredOldOpcodeTable[mid][0]) {
18126 break;
18127 }
18128 if (Opcode < getPredOldOpcodeTable[mid][0])
18129 end = mid;
18130 else
18131 start = mid + 1;
18132 }
18133 if (start == end)
18134 return -1; // Instruction doesn't exist in this table.
18135
18136 return getPredOldOpcodeTable[mid][1];
18137}
